short_description: The VECTOR_2_ORDERED_PAIR node returns the OrderedPair where x and y axes are the input nodes.

parameters.name: default
parameters.description: The input vector that will be the x axis of OrderedPair.

parameters.name: y
parameters.description: The input vector that will be the y axis of OrderedPair.

returns.description: The OrderedPair that is generated from the input vectors
